{"tid":402791,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"用左撕拉面膜之後，塊臉真係平左滑左好鬼多","createTime":"2017-09-16T16:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T10:18:41.000Z","uid":75100,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b94b80c0704844d972d1a582f1cb44ab3bc54ca8","tid":402791,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:29:08.000Z","msg":"牌子唔講啦，我都係淘寶既，見十幾萬人買我先夠薑試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔係任何牌子既打手，我相信韓國/香港/外國出既都應該有差唔多效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我本身皮膚都ok，但鼻有黑頭，同埋摸會有d卡手，摸到一粒粒咁，同埋有d黃。第一次驚，所以查左好少，等左30分鐘仲係得薄膜，好多斷位，拉得好唔爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但第一次半成功之後，個一刻係feel到塊臉白左，同埋d臉毛好似少左d，鼻平時好多黑頭，用力按都按唔出D黑頭，R個鼻又會有浸油脂味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但個一刻覺得個鼻&quot; 鬆左 &quot; 既感覺。<br />\n<br />\n呢類用品唔敢用太密，驚扯鬆毛孔，隔左5日之後再玩一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今次查得好重手，最後超完美由頭撕落尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但今次明顯扯既時候會痛，因為真係一塊面膜連住塊臉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 用完呢2次之後懶，無再用，但明顯成塊臉出少左油，個鼻鬆左，而家沖完涼，個鼻軟左一按就出到黑頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成塊臉仲係滑，至少滑過未用之前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e39ad8fab87ecded9d97dc9eb32da5309730604","tid":402791,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:30:31.000Z","msg":"Youtube有好多用家拍既片，有韓妹有大陸妹，可以隨便click一條睇下到底係咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最緊要，成塊撕出黎個陣真係又有成功感，又好爽快啊!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a34c4e400f5094e