g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個枝係邊度買都唔係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有效咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be350f204ca377fd5f92bacf614291fac10cfdb","tid":402791,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T02:46:25.000Z","msg":"我覺得撕拉面膜，超級月球爛面要慎用之外，基本普通人都應該用得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我既理解，主要係將你裡面既污槽野扯出黎，副就補下濕咁，所以唔可以成日用，同埋好似話成日用好多補野補唔入，都係因為裡面塞太多垃雜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我之前鼻有粒暗瘡? 都唔知係咪，好鬼耐，好似成舊野係皮膚下面咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 按落去就好痛，但吱佢係無野出，同埋痛到吱唔到。用左2次之後，最近發現好似唔見左，按個個位完全唔痛了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a722b89abf51ad66feb26aa3988f85228e7e2950","tid":402791,"uid":75100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T02:48:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊隻好用</blockquote><br />\n我諗sasa個d鋪應該有得買? <br />\n<br />\n我覺得你是但買隻中等價錢既應該都ok，呢類野都係幾十一百咁，好用程度應該唔會差好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da46841dec5f9e295a8d70ee507ce70c26c27425","tid":402791,"uid":96406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:30:04.000Z","msg":"有啲撕拉面膜無乜力 ， 之前用果隻一撕出黎 好似牛皮膠紙撕開咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee2455753b96f826b25ea226f16c685d79e4fda","tid":402791,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:18:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有啲撕拉面膜無乜力 ， 之前用果隻一撕出黎 好似牛皮膠紙撕開咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好驚扯鬆d皮，但扯個野真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}